  "detailed_description": "Piecing It Together brings jigsaw puzzles to a whole new dimension!<br>Construct 3D puzzles of beautiful dioramas, each brought to life by various artists.<br><br>The game provides a calm and meditative environment for you to enjoy.<br>There are no scores, timers, or meters to worry about. It's just you and your puzzle pieces!<br>Enjoy a quick puzzling session with just a handful of pieces, or challenge yourself with many!<br><br>Piecing It Together is a modern take on a classic pastime that’s fun for the whole family!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Each puzzle has 4 Difficulties, from 20 Pieces up to 200 Pieces<br></li><li> Meditative gameplay with no timers, meters or scores<br></li><li> Save and resume your progress at any time<br></li><li> Relax to our soundtrack inspired by Animal Crossing</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Push, pull, and rotate pieces to complete the puzzle!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/1e48ad8c31f46699a23bcf4125196678.poster.avif?t=1745696114\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/1e48ad8c31f46699a23bcf4125196678.webm?t=1745696114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/1e48ad8c31f46699a23bcf4125196678.mp4?t=1745696114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with real 3D puzzle pieces!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/751a699937e97c4fdb89df6cb5c218f0.poster.avif?t=1745696114\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/751a699937e97c4fdb89df6cb5c218f0.webm?t=1745696114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/751a699937e97c4fdb89df6cb5c218f0.mp4?t=1745696114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Piecing It Together brings jigsaw puzzles to a whole new dimension!<br>Construct 3D puzzles of beautiful dioramas, each brought to life by various artists.<br><br>The game provides a calm and meditative environment for you to enjoy.<br>There are no scores, timers, or meters to worry about. It's just you and your puzzle pieces!<br>Enjoy a quick puzzling session with just a handful of pieces, or challenge yourself with many!<br><br>Piecing It Together is a modern take on a classic pastime that’s fun for the whole family!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Each puzzle has 4 Difficulties, from 20 Pieces up to 200 Pieces<br></li><li> Meditative gameplay with no timers, meters or scores<br></li><li> Save and resume your progress at any time<br></li><li> Relax to our soundtrack inspired by Animal Crossing</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Push, pull, and rotate pieces to complete the puzzle!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/1e48ad8c31f46699a23bcf4125196678.poster.avif?t=1745696114\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/1e48ad8c31f46699a23bcf4125196678.webm?t=1745696114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/1e48ad8c31f46699a23bcf4125196678.mp4?t=1745696114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with real 3D puzzle pieces!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/751a699937e97c4fdb89df6cb5c218f0.poster.avif?t=1745696114\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665630/extras/751a699937e97c4fdb89df6cb5